<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:20:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾州长称将在台湾附近建设新岛屿港口，无需美国帮助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-build-new-islands-port-near-taiwan-without-us-help-governor-says-2024-03-22/</link><description>当地州长周五表示，美国军方不会参与台湾附近菲律宾最北端偏远岛屿的港口开发，从而消除了因美国在该地区存在而与中国发生摩擦的潜在根源。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-build-new-islands-port-near-taiwan-without-us-help-governor-says-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：零跑汽车将在波兰Stellantis工厂开始生产小型电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-start-production-small-ev-polish-stellantis-plant-2024-03-22/</link><description>两名知情人士周五告诉路透社，作为两家汽车制造商合资企业的一部分，中国零跑汽车将开始在波兰的 Stellantis 工厂生产小型电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-start-production-small-ev-polish-stellantis-plant-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权机构向已故中国异见人士致敬暴露分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/tribute-deceased-chinese-dissident-exposes-fractures-un-rights-body-2024-03-22/</link><description>周五，在联合国人权机构发生的一场紧张事件中，中国打断了多个非政府组织向已故中国人权活动人士致敬的企图，该事件暴露了西方国家与北京支持者之间的分歧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/tribute-deceased-chinese-dissident-exposes-fractures-un-rights-body-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>Netflix 的《三体问题》让中国观众瞠目结舌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/netflixs-3-body-problem-leaves-jaws-dropped-among-chinese-viewers-2024-03-22/</link><description>Netflix 改编的中国科幻经典作品《三体》在中国上映的第一天就吸引了大量观众，尽管中国还没有流媒体服务，并立即在社交媒体上引发了争论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/netflixs-3-body-problem-leaves-jaws-dropped-among-chinese-viewers-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞计划于 2024 年晚些时候开始在意大利销售汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-plans-start-selling-cars-italy-later-2024-2024-03-22/</link><description>奇瑞汽车意大利国家经理表示，奇瑞汽车将于第三季度开始在意大利销售Omoda和Jaecoo品牌汽车，使其成为中国集团的第二个欧洲市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-plans-start-selling-cars-italy-later-2024-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>卢比创历史新低，录得七个月来最大单周跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-hits-record-low-posts-steepest-weekly-fall-seven-months-2024-03-22/</link><description>交易商表示，周五印度卢比兑美元汇率跌至历史新低，受到离岸人民币贬值和接近尾盘时强劲的当地美元需求的压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:54:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-hits-record-low-posts-steepest-weekly-fall-seven-months-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>1-2月流入中国外资减少19.9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-investment-flows-into-china-shrink-199-jan-feb-2024-03-22/</link><description>商务部周五公布的数据显示，尽管政府正在加紧吸引外国企业，但今年 1 月至 2 月，流入中国的外国投资仍较去年同期减少 19.9%，至 2151 亿元人民币（合 300 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-investment-flows-into-china-shrink-199-jan-feb-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：央行猛烈攻击后美元飙升，苹果公司受挫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:08:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道称，由于电动汽车销量增长放缓，特斯拉削减了在中国的汽车产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trims-output-cars-china-amid-slower-ev-sales-growth-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-22/</link><description>据彭博社周五报道，特斯拉已经减少了中国工厂的汽车产量，因为这家美国电动汽车制造商正在努力应对需求放缓和市场激烈竞争的问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 09:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trims-output-cars-china-amid-slower-ev-sales-growth-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>美团第四季度收入增长22.6%，超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/meituan-beats-q4-revenue-expectations-2024-03-22/</link><description>中国食品配送巨头美团点评周五公布，季度收入增长 22.6%，超出预期，无视中国经济放缓的影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/meituan-beats-q4-revenue-expectations-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>在大型中国芯片展上，企业纷纷呼吁购买国产芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/major-china-chip-fair-firms-ramp-up-call-buy-domestic-2024-03-22/</link><description>中国半导体相关公司本周在该国最大的芯片行业展会之一上竭尽全力推销国内采购，呼应了北京方面为面临日益加剧的地缘政治压力的行业提供支持的呼吁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/major-china-chip-fair-firms-ramp-up-call-buy-domestic-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英国法律总局搁置中国营业执照计划并裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-licence-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</link><description>两位消息人士称，英国保险公司和资产管理公司 Legal &amp;amp; General 搁置了获得中国营业执照的计划，并将在岸员工人数减少了一半以上，加入了在不确定的市场中缩减规模的全球金融公司名单。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 06:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-licence-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚、英国呼吁中国支持香港、南海和俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/australia-britain-warn-potentially-devastating-consequences-israeli-operation-2024-03-22/</link><description>周五，在伦敦和堪培拉深化安全关系的会议后，澳大利亚和英国批评中国在香港、南海的行动以及对俄罗斯的支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 06:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/australia-britain-warn-potentially-devastating-consequences-israeli-operation-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国正在审查普华永道在恒大 780 亿美元欺诈案中所扮演的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-scrutinises-pwc-role-78-bln-evergrande-fraud-case-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-03-22/</link><description>据彭博社周五报道，在中国恒大集团被指控欺诈 780 亿美元后，中国当局正在审查普华永道 (PwC) 在该开发商会计实践中所扮演的角色。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-scrutinises-pwc-role-78-bln-evergrande-fraud-case-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英国法律总局搁置中国营业执照计划并裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</link><description>两位消息人士称，英国保险公司和资产管理公司 Legal &amp;amp; General 搁置了获得中国营业执照的计划，并将境内员工人数减少了一半以上，加入了在不确定的市场中缩减规模的全球金融公司名单。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>